name: Duskfall Project 3D Ultra
description:
Merged From:

  • Duskfall Project Virtual

  • Duskfall AI

  • Duskfall Portal Crew duskfalltest

If you like what we've got for our merged and other models consider donating: https://patreon.com/earthndusk

  • DO NOT SELL THIS MODEL, OR MERGES

  • Do merge, and do enjoy.

  • Generative images for commercial use are fine.

  • Credit in your merges would be great.

CONFIG IS REQUIRED and is actually from Project Unreal Engine which was merged into the other model. WebUI renames it after merging.

modelVersions.description: This brings more of the neko/catboys back in, and a larger focus on the facial structures we were used to in the first two models.
